title: Phitsanulok Songkwae F.C.
text: Phitsanulok Songkwae Football Club (<a href="Thai%20alphabet">Thai</a> สโมสรฟุตบอลพิษณุโลกสองแคว) is a <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a> semi professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Phitsanulok%20Province">Phitsanulok Province</a>. They currently play in <a href="Thai%20Football%20Amateur%20Tournament">Thai Football Amateur Tournament</a>.
